-- Ambani Says Reliance Industries Will Supply Gas to ADAG When Plants Ready
-- Natalie Obiko Pearson
-- 2010-06-18T05:53:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/ambani-says-reliance-industries-will-supply-gas-to-adag-when-plants-ready.html

          
          
             Reliance Industries Ltd., India’s
biggest company by market value, will supply gas to the Anil
Dhirubhai Ambani Group, or ADAG, when the group’s power plants
are ready, Chairman Mukesh Ambani said today at the company’s
shareholder meeting in Mumbai.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
